{"tid":942344,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"天荒愛到地老純屬奢侈期望","createTime":"2018-12-15T15:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T09:03:59.000Z","uid":60123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5102f3a5e26a7a65d78e26f19f68cb0cb9e3cd44","tid":942344,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"睇到/聽到呢句 唔知大家會諗起邊個呢？<br />\n我相信絕大部份人都係會諗起自己既初戀<br />\n<br />\n天真地諗過同對方一生一世 儲夠錢就買樓結婚 有個幸福家庭 開開心心一齊白頭偕老<br />\n<br />\n可惜種種原因 種種難關 種種誘惑<br />\n令到大家既初戀都係無疾而終<br />\n以為佢係special one, 點知佢都只係normal one<br />\n<br />\n大家又係點樣去捱過第一次分手呢個心理關口？不妨分享下各自既經歷"},{"pid":"5660c4b4c39f5266ecb578d6b0a2c894ddd06e7b","tid":942344,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"都算幾好笑"},{"pid":"0e055fc0fbdcfec719e7c92852e34e296feef39b","tid":942344,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5660c4b4c39f5266ecb578d6b0a2c894ddd06e7b","tid":942344,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"都算幾好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d8a0a43e52e36525333ba2fbb9baa259a3c0c8","tid":942344,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e055fc0fbdcfec719e7c92852e34e296feef39b","tid":942344,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5660c4b4c39f5266ecb578d6b0a2c894ddd06e7b","tid":942344,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"都算幾好笑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"終於<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />終於"},{"pid":"bd2beac887f749c9cd1b31cb25e94e837548c3e5","tid":942344,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc